txt.en: An infestation of foul crawlers is destroying the roots of healthy vegetation in Tâl Bruinen.
There are crawlers infesting Tâl Bruinen, in the Trollshaws.\n\nWhile in Tâl Bruinen, you should purge as many of the foul crawlers destroying the vegetation there as you can.
